00:05:31.600 --> 00:05:35.800
They're only 1 yen and 10 yen 
coins, but they're all real!

00:05:36.160 --> 00:05:39.690
Well done, you guys.

00:05:39.690 --> 00:05:42.790
Many a little makes a mickle.

00:05:42.790 --> 00:05:46.530
I think that's about five thousand yen.

00:05:48.910 --> 00:05:51.440
As long as I have you guys, Harvest,

00:05:51.440 --> 00:05:54.580
I'll never have to worry about money.

00:05:54.580 --> 00:05:57.240
Hey, that's the user?

00:05:57.240 --> 00:05:59.730
