00:08:56.590 --> 00:08:57.780
Okuyasu...

00:08:58.260 --> 00:09:00.010
Is something wrong with your left foot?

00:09:01.790 --> 00:09:03.530
Whoa, what?!

00:09:03.530 --> 00:09:06.800
