00:09:06.800 --> 00:09:09.760
Do they belong to you, Shigekiyo?

00:09:09.760 --> 00:09:11.510
I didn't even notice...

00:09:11.510 --> 00:09:13.110
Talk about stingy...

00:09:14.480 --> 00:09:17.820
Hey, I'll give you guys half of this.

00:09:17.820 --> 00:09:18.700
Huh?!

00:09:18.700 --> 00:09:22.830
You're my friends, right?
We have the same kind of power.

00:09:22.830 --> 00:09:24.680
R-Really?!

00:09:24.680 --> 00:09:26.150
Lucky us!

00:09:27.250 --> 00:09:29.610
