00:15:42.370 --> 00:15:44.170
That's awesome, Shigechi!

00:15:44.170 --> 00:15:48.510
Your Stand, Harvest, is really amazing!

00:15:48.510 --> 00:15:51.850
Y-You really think it's amazing?

00:15:51.850 --> 00:15:56.980
