compliment me much...

00:15:56.980 --> 00:15:59.020
Do you really think I'm amazing?

00:15:59.020 --> 00:16:01.780
Hey, have a little more confidence, Shigechi.

00:16:01.780 --> 00:16:04.880
This is something that only you can do.

00:16:04.880 --> 00:16:07.780
Okuyasu... Josuke...

00:16:08.090 --> 00:16:09.190
Straighten.

